pageContext.claim: “March 5th is rapidly approaching and the Democrats are doing nothing about DACA. They Resist, Blame, Complain and Obstruct - and do nothing. Start pushing Nancy Pelosi and the Dems to work out a DACA fix, NOW!”
pageContext.analysis: Democrats came to Trump with a bipartisan plan that had been crafted in the Senate, so clearly there is an effort to find a solution on DACA, or Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals. Trump rejected it.
